org.shanerx.faketrollplus.utils.function

Interface Test

  • Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface Test
    Used for internal argument validation purposes. Same concept as Predicate, but does not take a parameter. Another difference is that test() returns false when the result is positive.
